content.rendered:
Clinic LPN | Tulsa, Oklahoma
  • Full-Time and PRN positions available
  • Will assist physician in the clinic back office duties
  • Must have 2+ years current LPN working experience
  • Must have Oklahoma LPN license in good standing
  • Compensation is dependent on experience
  • $16-$18/hour
